---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="2-Bedroom Granny Flats Frankston & Peninsula | $140K-$220K | (03) 9003 0108"
  description="2-bedroom granny flats for Frankston, Mt Eliza, Mornington and the Peninsula. 60-90m² for couples, parents+teen, or long-term rental. Full kitchen, two bedrooms. Free consultation."
  canonical="https://frankstongrannyflats.com.au/services/two-bedroom/">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">For couples, families, rental</span>
      <h1>2-Bedroom granny flats in <span class="accent">Frankston &amp; the Peninsula</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        60&ndash;90m&sup2; of self-contained living &mdash; enough for a couple, a parent
        with a teen, or a family-sized long-term rental. Crosses the 60m&sup2; VicSmart
        threshold so usually needs a full planning permit (3 months), but unlocks
        rental returns the 1-bed can&rsquo;t.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book a free consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>When 2-bedroom is the right call.</h2>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Couples and parents-plus-child.</h3>
        <p>
          A 1-bedroom doesn&rsquo;t cut it for two unrelated people. A 2-bedroom granny
          flat with bedrooms at opposite ends gives parents and a teen, two siblings,
          or carer-plus-client real separation. Privacy matters more than floor area.
          Most 2-bed plans we design have a 9&ndash;12m&sup2; second bedroom &mdash;
          enough for a single bed, wardrobe, desk.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Long-term rental returns.</h3>
        <p>
          A 2-bedroom self-contained on the Mornington Peninsula rents long-term
          at $480&ndash;$650/week in 2026 depending on suburb. A $180K all-in 2-bed
          modular at $550/week = $28,600 gross rental p.a., ~$22K net after expenses.
          7&ndash;9 year payback period before capital gain. The numbers don&rsquo;t
          work on a 1-bed at $400/week rent; they do work on a 2-bed.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">The planning permit reality.</h3>
        <p>
          Almost all 2-bedroom builds exceed the <strong>60m&sup2; VicSmart limit</strong>
          and need a full planning permit. Expect 60&ndash;90 days for Frankston City,
          90&ndash;120 days for Mornington Peninsula Shire (especially overlay-affected
          sites). The permit cost is in the $4K&ndash;$8K range. We sequence the
          design, NatHERS pre-assessment, and permit lodgement to overlap with the
          build prep so total project time is 6&ndash;9 months.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Modular 2-bed vs custom 2-bed.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Modular 2-bed 60&ndash;75m&sup2;:</strong> $140K&ndash;$185K. Most factories produce a single core 2-bed plan with 2&ndash;3 variations. Faster, cheaper. Crane access required (won&rsquo;t fit tight Carrum Downs blocks).</li>
          <li><strong>Custom on-site 2-bed 70&ndash;90m&sup2;:</strong> $180K&ndash;$220K. Bespoke floor plan, architectural match to main house, fits any block geometry. Best for Mt Eliza, Frankston South, Mornington heritage areas.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">2-bedroom standard spec inclusions.</h3>
        <p>Same as 1-bed but bigger, plus:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Two bedrooms (typically 11m&sup2; main, 9m&sup2; second)</li>
          <li>Walk-in robe in main bedroom where layout allows</li>
          <li>Larger bathroom (often with separate WC for two-bedroom rental flexibility)</li>
          <li>Larger kitchen (1800mm bench instead of 1500mm)</li>
          <li>Separate dedicated parking bay (Frankston City + Peninsula Shire both require)</li>
          <li>Second-zone ducted heating where layout is &gt;9m end-to-end</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Where we work.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/frankston-south/">Frankston South</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/mt-eliza/">Mt Eliza</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/mornington/">Mornington</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/carrum-downs/">Carrum Downs</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/seaford/">Seaford</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/mornington-peninsula/">Full Peninsula</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free 2-bedroom design consultation.</h2>
        <p>On-site visit, rental yield calc included if relevant. Fixed quote in 7 days.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
